        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 12. Cigclisula australis n. sp. A–F, USNM 8894, holotype, Australia. A, group of zooids and spatulate interzooidal avicularia. B, primary orifice. C, ovicelled zooid. D, E, F, ovicelled zooids with suboral avicularia and an associated spatulate interzooidal avicularium. Scale bars: A, C, D, E, F = 200 µm; B = 50 µm." ;
